OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Flikely through the evening.
OL,7,FTemperatures quickly falling overnight
OL,8,Fwith frost likely in rural areas.
OL,9,FCloud thickens in the early hours,
OL,10,Fallowing some recovery in temperatures
OL,11,Fand bringing sporadic light rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FVariable cloud and patchy
OL,14,Frain possible for much of the day,
OL,15,Fwith occasional bright or sunny
OL,16,Fintervals. Breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
